<div class="dablink">"World conquest" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/World_domination_(disambiguation)" title="World domination (disambiguation)">World domination (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<p><b>World domination</b> (sometimes <b>world conquest</b>, <b>global domination</b>, or <a href="/wiki/Colloquial" title="Colloquial" class="mw-redirect">colloquially</a> <b>taking over the world</b>), in which a single political authority rules over all the inhabitants of planet Earth, has been attempted by several individuals and political systems throughout history, and remains a popular theme in fiction.</p>
